name: Spread the Love
description:
Spread the love, not hate. Stop the stigma and be kind to each other. Because we all are the same as human beings.

The world commemorates WORLD AIDS Day on December 1st, and I want to share this positive message. And  all the primary sales of this NFT will be given to the local HIV/AIDS foundations.

40 editions of this artworks were made because it's been 40 years years since HIV/AIDS was first identified.

2300 x 2300 px
